# Admin UI is built by frontend-maven-plugin from apps/admin-ui/out/ at every
# Maven build; nothing should ever live under src/main/resources/static for
# ingress-auth-service. (Stale checked-in chunks caused the v20260505 "Edit URL
# invisible" bug because they shadowed the fresh build.)
services/ingress-auth-service/src/main/resources/static/
